flowchart TD
    A[Start: Hypotheses and required tables/time window] --> B[Run checks from scripts/qa_checks.sql]
    B --> C[Save instantiated SQL to queries/00_qa-*.sql]
    C --> D[Evaluate findings by check group]
    D --> E[Assign severities per finding]
    E --> F[Use references/severity-examples.md for borderline calls]
    F --> G{Any CRITICAL findings?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Block analysis and define mitigation options]
    G -->|No| I[Compute quality score and caveats]
    H --> J[Write results/qa/qa-report.md and results/qa/qa-summary.json]
    I --> J
    J --> K[Save QA query outputs to results/qa/*.csv]
    K --> L{Need pandas handling for QA outputs?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Route via .cursor/skills/pandas-operations/SKILL.md and load only needed references/* file]
    L -->|No| N[Proceed]
    M --> N
    N --> O[Checkpoint: proceed to EDA?]
